===Noun===
'''elephantiasis'''

#{{pathology}} A complication of [[chronic]] [[filariasis]], in which [[nematode]] worms block the [[lymphatic]] vessels, usually in the legs or [[scrotum]], causing extreme enlargement of the infected area.

